## Summary

Ports the cumulative dependency-canvas performance work from
[self-evolving/lean-workspace-template#19](https://github.com/self-evolving/lean-workspace-template/pull/19)
and [#20](https://github.com/self-evolving/lean-workspace-template/pull/20) to the hosted
140-node Sphere Packing blueprint.

- shares SVG arrow markers instead of emitting one marker definition per edge;
- removes redundant edge markup and repeated inline card-action SVGs;
- replaces per-card hover listeners with delegated, indexed neighborhood updates;
- keeps selection and hover focus rendering separate;
- batches high-frequency drag, wheel, and pinch rendering to one animation frame;
- caches interaction geometry at frame/gesture scope and hardens cancellation cleanup;
- adds 21 canvas regressions and ensures the existing explicit CI test list includes them.

The active vendored plugin is edited directly and every change is documented in
`PATCHES.md`.

## Sphere fixture impact

For the existing 140-node / 287-edge canvas:

- DOM elements: 3,087 → 1,384 (−55.2%);
- raw generated HTML: 324,951 → 225,180 bytes (−30.7%);
- gzip: 32,805 → 29,434 bytes (−10.3%).

Deterministic interaction tests also reduce three drag writes to one, two wheel reads/writes
to one read/write, and two pinch reads/writes to one gesture read/write.

These are static and deterministic operation measurements, not inferred frame-time claims.
The upstream stack still tracks the final foreground DevTools trace and visual smoke checks.

## Scope

Exactly seven files are changed:

- `package.json` (only `scripts.test`);
- `scripts/run-tests.mjs`;
- `quartz/plugins/local/canvas-page/PATCHES.md`;
- `quartz/plugins/local/canvas-page/dist/index.js`;
- `canvas-page.test.mjs`;
- `canvas-focus.test.mjs`;
- `canvas-interaction.test.mjs`.

The `.canvas` file was not regenerated. This PR does not change canvas data, lockfiles,
workflows, typings, source maps, Quartz configuration, or plugin shims.

## Validation

Passed with Node 22.17.0:

- canvas suites: 21/21;
- existing explicit CI Quartz invocation: 25/25 after automatic canvas-suite inclusion;
- clean-cache `npm run build` against the 140-node fixture;
- `git diff --check`.

Known unrelated failures remain intentionally out of scope:

- bare `npm test` has one stale `BlueprintGraph.test.mjs` assertion tied to removed demo content;
- `npm run check` reports pre-existing Prettier issues in `blueprint.config.json` and `scripts/lib/blueprint-model.mjs`;
- the existing extraction workflow can fail because plain `lake build` has no default workspace target.

